msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Every case has one last element to bring the class\n"
"trial to an end. This is the <CLT><CLT 3>Closing Argument<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>In this phase, you'll give a <CLT><CLT 3>complete summary of the\n"
"case<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>You'll have to reproduce the flow of events for the\n"
"case in the form of a <CLT><CLT 3>comic book<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>However, you'll notice that in the comic, there are a\n"
"number of <CLT><CLT 3>pieces<CLT><CLT 23> missing.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>It's up to you to <CLT><CLT 3>complete the comic<CLT><CLT 23> using the\n"
"provided <CLT><CLT 3>Truth Panels<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Also, if you take aim at a missing section and press\n"
"the <CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_RECONSTRUCT_HINT%<CLT><CLT 23>...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Holy cow! You'll get a <CLT><CLT 3>hint<CLT><CLT 23> that might lead to a\n"
"breakthrough!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Well then...good luck, and have fun!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>The <CLT><CLT 3>Closing Argument<CLT><CLT 23> is about to begin. Would you\n"
"like to hear more?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
